<div class="container mt-4">
    <h2>Creating a Microsoft Azure Account</h2>

    <p>Microsoft Azure is a powerful cloud computing platform. Creating an account is your first step to exploring its services.</p>

    <h3>Step 1: Navigate to the Azure Website</h3>
    <p>Go to <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/" target="_blank">azure.microsoft.com</a>.</p>
    <img src="~/images/azure-homepage.png" alt="Azure Homepage" class="img-fluid mb-3" />

    <h3>Step 2: Start Your Free Azure Account</h3>
    <p>Click the "Start free" or "Free account" button.</p>
    <img src="~/images/azure-start-free.png" alt="Start Free Button" class="img-fluid mb-3" />

    <h3>Step 3: Sign In or Create a Microsoft Account</h3>
    <p>Sign in with your Microsoft account or create a new one.</p>
    <img src="~/images/microsoft-signin.png" alt="Microsoft Sign In" class="img-fluid mb-3" />

    <h3>Step 4: Provide Your Information</h3>
    <p>Enter your personal details and verify your phone number.</p>
    <img src="~/images/azure-personal-info.png" alt="Personal Info Form" class="img-fluid mb-3" />

    <h3>Step 5: Verify Your Identity</h3>
    <p>Verify your identity with a credit or debit card. (No charges unless you upgrade.)</p>
    <img src="~/images/azure-card-verify.png" alt="Card Verification" class="img-fluid mb-3" />

    <h3>Step 6: Agree to the Terms and Conditions</h3>
    <p>Read and accept the terms and conditions.</p>
    <img src="~/images/azure-terms.png" alt="Terms and Conditions" class="img-fluid mb-3" />

    <h3>Step 7: Access the Azure Portal</h3>
    <p>You'll be redirected to the Azure portal.</p>
    <img src="~/images/azure-portal.png" alt="Azure Portal" class="img-fluid mb-3" />

    <h3>Step 8: Exploring the Azure Portal (Optional)</h3>
    <p>Explore the Azure portal and start creating resources.</p>

    <p>Congratulations! You've created your Azure account.</p>
</div>